---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What makes GirokIQ different from other note apps?",
    answer: "GirokIQ is a native iPadOS app that combines the structure of linear notes with the freedom of an infinite canvas. It's built specifically for deep work and creative thinking, without the distractions of traditional tools."
  },
  {
    question: "Does it support handwriting?",
    answer: "Yes! We use native PencilKit integration for a pressure-sensitive, incredibly natural feel. It's optimized specifically for Apple Pencil on iPad."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I organize multiple notebooks?",
    answer: "Absolutely. You can create unlimited notebooks, organize them into nested folders, and sync everything securely across your devices via our cloud backend."
  },
  {
    question: "Are there AI features?",
    answer: "Yes, AI is already a core feature. We include multiple distinct AI models built directly into the app—each tailored for specific tasks like summarizing, brainstorming, or structuring your notes. No API key setup required."
  }
];
---

<section class="py-24 bg-dark-bg">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-8">
      {faqs.map(faq => (
        <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">{faq.question}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">{faq.answer}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
